WEBVTT

00:05.105 --> 00:06.705
( Korie )
Willie, are you as
excited as I am

00:06.806 --> 00:07.773
about your
reunion this weekend ?

00:07.841 --> 00:09.074
                       ( Jase )
                       Reunion ?

00:09.175 --> 00:10.743
            Willie, do I have to
            remind you

00:10.844 --> 00:12.778
     how much you've
     changed since high school ?

00:12.846 --> 00:15.080
He still looks
the same.
                   ( laughing )

00:15.181 --> 00:16.648
                    Are you
                    kidding me ?

00:16.750 --> 00:19.118
         You have to say that
         'cause you married him.

00:19.219 --> 00:21.487
           ( Willie )
    Around here, high school
    reunions are a big deal.

00:21.588 --> 00:24.823
   It's a great opportunity to
show off how successful you are,

00:24.924 --> 00:26.825
  how smoking hot your wife is

00:26.926 --> 00:29.328
       and how little hair
          you've lost.

00:29.396 --> 00:30.729
           I'm looking
         forward to it.

00:30.830 --> 00:31.964
                   We're going
                   dove hunting.

00:32.031 --> 00:33.265
                You need to come
                with us.

00:33.366 --> 00:34.833
              You'll have
              a way better time.

00:34.934 --> 00:36.802
He needs to go to his
high school reunion.

00:36.870 --> 00:38.404
It's a big deal.
            I didn't go to mine.

00:38.505 --> 00:39.905
           I went frog-hunting.

00:40.006 --> 00:42.107
        Here's my take on
      high school reunions.

00:42.208 --> 00:44.343
   If I haven't contacted you

00:44.411 --> 00:46.578
      in the last 20 years,

00:46.679 --> 00:48.680
        there's probably
       a reason for that.

00:48.782 --> 00:50.315
              They're not gonna
              know who you were.

00:50.417 --> 00:52.317
                I mean, you are
                unrecognizable.

00:52.419 --> 00:53.519
          What are you
      talking about, son ?

00:53.586 --> 00:55.320
                 This just looks
                 like a kid.

00:55.422 --> 00:57.356
          Now, you look like...

00:57.424 --> 00:59.158
               the sasquatch
               who ate this guy.

01:00.493 --> 01:01.860
                  ( laughing )

01:01.961 --> 01:03.595
       Hey, all I've done
        is grown a beard.

01:03.696 --> 01:05.564
                 And added about
                 a "hundo."

01:05.665 --> 01:07.032
  Jase.
          I haven't gained
             100 pounds.

01:07.133 --> 01:08.267
            Have you
        lost your mind ?

01:08.334 --> 01:09.768
               You're sucking in
               your gut.

01:09.869 --> 01:11.403
         I'm not sucking
            crap in.

01:11.504 --> 01:13.005
            Everybody
    picks up a little weight.

01:13.073 --> 01:14.373
       It's solid weight.

01:14.441 --> 01:16.275
I like a man with
a little meat on his bones.

01:16.342 --> 01:17.376
           Well, let me tell you
           something.

01:17.444 --> 01:20.279
           You hit the jackpot.

01:20.346 --> 01:22.881
       "I like a man with
  a little meat on his bones" ?

01:22.982 --> 01:25.284
       That's polite for,
          "You're fat."

01:25.351 --> 01:27.019
            That boy is
            in there, somewhere,

01:27.087 --> 01:28.520
              screaming, saying,
              "Let me out.

01:28.621 --> 01:29.855
              I've been eaten."

01:29.956 --> 01:32.091
            ( Jase )
    Willie then... handsome.

01:32.158 --> 01:34.793
      Willie now... rotund.

01:34.894 --> 01:36.028
      I've gotten muscular.

01:36.096 --> 01:37.396
                  ( laughing )

01:37.464 --> 01:39.398
    His dimples went from his
          upper cheeks

01:39.466 --> 01:40.899
      to his lower cheeks.

01:41.000 --> 01:42.401
        Don't you need to
          go to work ?

01:42.469 --> 01:44.303
           I'm just trying to
           save you some misery.

01:44.370 --> 01:45.370
We're gonna have fun,
Willie.

01:45.438 --> 01:46.705
It's gonna be great.

01:46.806 --> 01:48.407
        Well, you better get
        ready for the fat jokes.

01:48.475 --> 01:50.275
        Get out of here.
          'Cause they're coming.

01:52.979 --> 01:54.546
          ♪ Silk suit

01:54.647 --> 01:56.448
          ♪ Black tie

01:56.549 --> 02:00.285
         ♪ I don't need
         a reason why ♪

02:00.386 --> 02:03.689
       ♪ They come running
   just as fast as they can ♪

02:03.756 --> 02:05.190
      ♪ 'Cause every girl's
             crazy ♪

