            ( Si )
            I'm having a problem
            with my dog.

10:00.967 --> 10:02.867
           He won't bring
           the doves back to me.

10:02.969 --> 10:04.603
           I think he's doing it
           for spite.

10:04.704 --> 10:07.372
Me and him have
a personality issue.

10:07.440 --> 10:09.274
Well, I don't know about
personality.

10:09.342 --> 10:11.343
We've got lots of
dogs here to choose from.

10:11.444 --> 10:13.678
We've got young dogs,
we've got old dogs.

10:13.779 --> 10:15.680
Different breeds of dogs.

